### health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### system info
GET http://localhost:8080/api/system/info
X-Request-Id: local-dev-request

### inspect get
GET http://localhost:8080/api/http/inspect?source=rest-client
X-Demo-Header: deploy-lab
Authorization: Bearer secret

### inspect post
POST http://localhost:8080/api/http/inspect
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token=secret

{
  "message": "hello deploy lab"
}

### create message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "部署记录",
  "content": "第一次原生部署成功"
}

### list messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/messages?limit=50

### delete message
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/messages/1

### request records
GET http://localhost:8080/api/request-records

### delay
GET http://localhost:8080/api/diagnostics/delay?milliseconds=1000

### status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/diagnostics/status?code=503

### error
GET http://localhost:8080/api/diagnostics/error
